<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Coding is Magic! ✨</title>
    <style>
        /* Base Styling */
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f8ff; /* Light Sky Blue */
            color: #4a4a4a;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 40px;
            margin: 0;
            overflow-x: hidden; /* Keeps the bird within the screen width */
            position: relative;
        }

        /* --- Cloud Generator --- */
        .cloud {
            position: absolute;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 50px;
            opacity: 0.8;
            z-index: -1; /* Puts clouds behind the main content */
        }
        .cloud::after, .cloud::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }
        
        /* Cloud shapes and positions */
        .c1 { width: 100px; height: 40px; top: 10%; left: 10%; }
        .c1::after { width: 50px; height: 50px; top: -25px; left: 15px; }
        .c1::before { width: 40px; height: 40px; top: -15px; left: 50px; }

        .c2 { width: 150px; height: 60px; top: 25%; right: 15%; transform: scale(1.2); }
        .c2::after { width: 70px; height: 70px; top: -35px; left: 25px; }
        .c2::before { width: 60px; height: 60px; top: -25px; left: 70px; }

        .c3 { width: 80px; height: 30px; bottom: 20%; left: 20%; opacity: 0.5; }
        .c3::after { width: 40px; height: 40px; top: -20px; left: 10px; }

        /* --- Flying Bird (Emoji + Animation) --- */
        .bird-container {
            position: absolute;
            top: 15%; /* Height of the bird's flight path */
            z-index: 10;
            font-size: 2rem; /* Size of the bird */
            
            /* The animation instruction */
            animation: flyAcross 15s linear infinite; 
        }

        /* Keyframes: Define the path from left to right */
        @keyframes flyAcross {
            0% { left: -10%; transform: translateY(0px) scaleX(1); } /* Start off-screen left */
            45% { transform: translateY(-20px) scaleX(1); } /* Slight wobble up */
            50% { transform: translateY(0px) scaleX(1); } /* Middle of screen */
            55% { transform: translateY(20px) scaleX(1); } /* Slight wobble down */
            100% { left: 110%; transform: translateY(0px) scaleX(1); } /* End off-screen right */
        }

        /* Container for the content */
        .container {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9); /* Semi-transparent white */
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 100%;
            backdrop-filter: blur(5px); /* Blurs the clouds behind the card slightly */
            margin-top: 100px; /* Space for the bird to fly above */
        }

        h1 {
            color: #6da9e4; /* Sky blue matching the vibe */
            text-align: center;
        }

        .step {
            background-color: #fffaf0; /* Light cream */
            margin: 15px 0;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            border-left: 5px solid #ffe4b5;
        }

        button {
            background-color: #6da9e4;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: bold;
            display: block;
            margin: 20px auto;
            transition: transform 0.2s, background-color 0.2s;
        }

        button:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
            background-color: #559ad9;
        }

        footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 0.8em;
            color: #888;
            z-index: 1;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="cloud c1"></div>
    <div class="cloud c2"></div>
    <div class="cloud c3"></div>

    <div class="bird-container">
        🐦
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>Coding is Magic! ✨</h1>
        <p>Coding is just giving instructions to a computer. Here is the secret recipe:</p>

        <div class="step">
            <strong>Step 1: Pick a Language 🍦</strong>
            <p>Try Python (for logic) or HTML/CSS (for building websites like this!)</p>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
            <strong>Step 2: Get a Code Editor 📝</strong>
            <p>Download VS Code—it's like a fancy notebook for your code.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
            <strong>Step 3: Break Things! 🔨</strong>
            <p>The best way to learn is to write code, see it break, and fix it.</p>
        </div>

        <button onclick="celebrate()">Click for Encouragement!</button>
    </div>

    <footer>Made with ✨ and Code</footer>

    <script>
        function celebrate() {
            alert("The sky is the limit! You're going to be an amazing coder! 🌟🐦");
        }
    </script>

</body>
</html>
